Detailed Description

The Particle Swarm Optimization algorithm.

The PSO class holds all the parameters and selects the function to be optimized.

bool PSO::noisyFirstComparePbestValues [private]

Only if pbest is better than the predecessor, the re-evaluation is done (default: false).

The current pbest value (average or single evaluation) is compared with the parent, if it is better, then the re-evaluation triggered by noisyBirdIsBetter is initiated.
